You look to me to speak.
你们指望我讲话。

1038
02:14:44,500 --> 02:14:47,795
I know not what to say other than we have all known too much death.
我不知道该说什么，除了我们都太熟悉的死亡。

1039
02:14:49,463 --> 02:14:52,215
